These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, mah-jongg, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
3. the person playing domino is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino | chess | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, cat, pony
1. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
2. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the cat##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Pet   | horse | cat | lizard | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, train, jet-ski, ship
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Transport   | roller | ship | train | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, pumpkin, banana
1. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person eating avocado##7
2. the person eating banana is not to the right of the person eating pumpkin##8
3. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating pumpkin is not to the right of the person eating artichoke##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Food   | avocado | banana | pumpkin | artichoke |

